]], [[blue]]\n|}\n\n===Buddhism and Hinduism===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!'''Coat of arms'''\n!'''Country'''\n!'''Religious characteristics'''\n|-\n| [[File:Bhutan emblem.svg|25px]]\n| [[Bhutan]] ([[Emblem of Bhutan|coat of arms]])\n| [[Druk]], [[Nelumbo nucifera|Lotus]]\n|-\n| [[File:Royal arms of Cambodia.svg|25px]]\n| [[Cambodia]] ([[Emblem of Cambodia|coat of arms]])\n| [[Om]]\n|-\n| [[File:Emblem of India.svg|25px]]\n| [[India]] ([[State Emblem of India|coat of arms]])\n| [[Ashoka Chakra]], [[Lion Capital of Ashoka]], [[Satyameva Jayate]]\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of Arms of Indonesia Garuda Pancasila.svg|25px]]\n| [[Indonesia]] ([[National emblem of Indonesia|coat of arms]])\n| [[Garuda]]\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of Laos.svg|25px]]\n| [[Laos]] ([[Emblem of Laos|coat of arms]])\n| [[Pha That Luang]]\n|-\n| [[File:State emblem of Mongolia.svg|25px]]\n| [[Mongolia]] ([[Emblem of Mongolia|coat of arms]])\n| [[Dharmachakra]], [[Ratnatraya]], [[Wind Horse]]\n|-\n| [[File:State seal of Myanmar.svg|25px]]\n| [[Myanmar]] ([[State seal of Myanmar|coat of arms]])\n| [[Chinthe]]\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of Nepal.svg|25px]]\n| [[Nepal]] ([[Emblem of Nepal|coat of arms]])\n| [[Janani Janmabhumishcha Swargadapi Gariyasi]]\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of Sri Lanka.svg|25px]]\n| [[Sri Lanka]] ([[Emblem of Sri Lanka|coat of arms]])\n| [[Dharmachakra]], [[Nelumbo nucifera|Lotus]]\n|-\n| [[File:Garuda Emblem of Thailand.svg|25px]]\n| [[Thailand]] ([[Emblem of Thailand|coat of arms]])\n| [[Garuda]]\n\n|}\n\n===Taoism and Confucianism===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!'''Coat of arms'''\n!'''Country'''\n!'''Religious characteristics'''\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of South Korea.svg|25px]]\n| [[South Korea]] ([[Emblem of South Korea|coat of arms]])\n| [[Yin and yang]]\n|}\n\n===Traditional===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!'''Coat of arms'''\n!'''Country'''\n!'''Religious characteristics'''\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of Argentina.svg|25px]]\n| [[Argentina]] ([[Coat of arms of Argentina|