end' (shortened to 'In Defens')\n|-\n|[[File:Great Seal of the United States (reverse).svg|25px]]\n| [[United States]] ([[Great Seal of the United States|seal]] reverse)\n|[[Eye of Providence]]\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of the Vatican City.svg|25px]]\n| [[Vatican City]] ([[Coats of arms of the Holy See and Vatican City|coat of arms]])\n| The crossed [[Key (lock)|keys]] of [[Saint Peter]] and the [[Papal Tiara]]\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of Arms of Vanuatu.svg|25px]]\n| [[Vanuatu]] ([[Coat of arms of Vanuatu|coat of arms]])\n| 'Long God yumi stanap' ('In God we stand')\n|}\n\n===Islam===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!'''Coat of arms'''\n!'''Country'''\n!'''Religious characteristics'''\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of Afghanistan.svg|25px]]\n| [[Afghanistan]] ([[Emblem of Afghanistan|coat of arms]])\n| [[Shahadah]], [[mosque]], [[mehrab]], [[Prayer rug]]\n|-\n| [[File:Seal of Algeria.svg|25px]]\n| [[Algeria]] ([[Emblem of Algeria|coat of arms]])\n| [[Star and crescent]]\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of Azerbaijan.svg|25px]]\n| [[Azerbaijan]] ([[Emblem of Azerbaijan|coat of arms]])\n| Calligraphic representation of the name [[Allah]] in the form of an [[eternal flame]], [[green]]\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of Bahrain.svg|25px]]\n| [[Bahrain]] ([[Coat of arms of Bahrain|coat of arms]])\n| five points represent the five pillars of Islam\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of Brunei.svg|25px]]\n| [[Brunei]] ([[Emblem of Brunei|coat of arms]])\n| [[Hilal (crescent moon)|Crescent moon]], \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0627\u0626\u0645\u0648\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u062d\u0633\u0646\u0648\u0646 \u0628\u0627\u0644\u0647\u062f\u0649 (Always in service with God's guidance)\n|-\n| [[File:Seal of the Comoros.svg|25px]]\n| [[Comoros]] ([[National seal of the Union of the Comoros|Seal]])\n| [[Star and crescent]]\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of Guinea-new.svg|25px]]\n| [[Guinea]] ([[Coat of arms of Guinea|coat of arms]])\n| [[Dove]]\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of Iran.svg|25px]]\n| [[Iran]] ([[Emblem of Iran|coat of arms]])\n| Name of Allah\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms (emblem) of Iraq 2008.svg|25px]]\n| [[Iraq]] ([[Coat of arms of Iraq|coat of arms]])\n| \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0623\u0643\u0628\u0631 (God is Great)\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of Arms of Jordan.svg|25px]]\n| [[Jordan]] ([[Coat of arms of Jordan|coat of arms]])\n| Its colours of the eagle signifies the banner of the Prophet Mohammad,  the globe signifies the emergence of Islamic civilisation,  \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0627\u062c\u064a \u0645\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0648\u0641\u064a\u0642 \u0648\u0627\u0644\u0639\u0648\u0646 (Who seeks support and guidance from God)\n|-\n| [[File:The emblem on the passport of Libya.svg|25px]]\n| [[Libya]] ([[Coat of arms of Libya|coat of arms]])\n| [[Star and crescent]]\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of Malaysia.svg|25px]]\n| [[Malaysia]] ([[Coat of arms of Malaysia|coat of arms]])\n| [[Hilal (crescent moon)|Crescent moon]]\n|-\n| [[File:Emblem of Maldives.svg|25px]]\n| [[Maldives]] ([[Emblem of Maldives|Emblem]])\n| [[Star and crescent]]\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of Mali.svg|25px]]\n| [[Mali]] ([[Coat of arms of Mali|coat of arms]])\n| [[Great Mosque of Djenn\u00e9]], Un Peuple, Un But, Une Foi (One People, One Goal, One Faith)\n|-\n| [[File:Seal of Mauritania.svg|25px]]\n| [[Mauritania]] ([[Seal of Mauritania|coat of arms]])\n| [[Star and crescent]], [[green]]\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of Morocco.svg|25px]]\n| [[Morocco]] ([[Coat of arms of Morocco|coat of arms]])\n| \u0625\u0646 \u062a\u0646\u0635\u0631\u0648\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u064a\u0646\u0635\u0631\u0643\u0645 (If you glorify God, he will glorify you)\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of Pakistan.svg|25px]]\n| [[Pakistan]] ([[State emblem of Pakistan|coat of arms]])\n|{{Script/Nastaliq|{{Nastaliq|\u0627\u06cc\u0645\u0627\u0646 \u060c \u0627\u062a\u062d\u0627\u062f \u060c \u0646\u0638\u0645}}}} (Faith, Unity, Discipline), [[Star and crescent]], [[green]]\n|-\n| [[File:Coat of arms of Senegal.svg|25px]]\n| 